    <p class="description">A domain name that exactly replicates a target search keyword — like <strong>bestplumberaustin.com</strong> or <strong>cheapcarinsurance.com</strong>. Once a powerful ranking shortcut, now a minor signal that backfires without genuine content quality.</p>
